    "created_at": "2015-07-16T09:20:30Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-16T09:20:30Z",
    "body": "Also the return values of `BrowserWindow.getSize()` and `BrowserWindow.getContentSize()` are different in frameless window(The behavior still looks like in frame window).\n\n```\nwin = new BrowserWindow({\n   width:800,\n   height: 600,\n   frame: false\n});\n\n// returns [800, 600]\nwin.getContentSize();\n\n// returns [800, 622]\nwin.getSize();\n```\n"
